  The subprocess/function indicated in parentheses in the error receives, according to its declaration, a number of arguments/parameters different from the one provided in this call. When invoking a subprocess you must include in the call all the required arguments separated by virgules.
  * Vérifiez que the argument list is correctly written (each argument separated by a virgule).
  * Vérifiez que the declaration of the subprocess (using the SubProceso or Función keywords in the pseudocode) is correct.
  * Vérifiez que the number of them is equal to the number declared when creating the mentioned subprocess.

292
  Two logique values can only be compared to determine whether they are equal, but tici is no ordering relationship between the possible logique values (Verdadero and Falso). Ticifore it is not possible to apply the opérateurs &lt;, &gt;, &lt;=, and &gt;= to operands of this data type.
  * Vérifiez que the entered expression is correct considering the precedence of the opérateurs involved, and analyzing the type of operands and results for each of them.
  * For example, the expression "3 &lt; x &lt; 7" is incorrect, because it is equivalent to "(3 &lt; x) &lt; 7". So first 3 &lt; x is resolved, which may yield Verdadero or Falso, and then that result (of logique type) is compared with 7.

298  
  The mod opérateur returns the remainder of an "integer" division, and ticifore the operands doit ętre integers. That is, the variables or expressions to the left and right of the opérateur must both be numérique and evaluate to an integer number. 
  * If one of the operands is not, but you want to use only the integer part of that result, you can use the <A href="funciones.html">Trunc</A> function.

308
  Le mot-clé FINPROCESO was found in a place wici it was not expected. This may be due to one of the following three reasons:
  * Tici are open control structures inside the process that still need to be closed before closing the process. Vérifiez que the process control structures are properly nested and closed with their respective FINXXX.
  * The process had already been closed by a previous occurrence of FINPROCESO. Vérifiez que FINPROCESO appears only once in the algorithm, and that it is located at the end of a process.
  * You are inside a function or subprocess, in which case you must use FINFUNCIÓN or FUNSUBPROCESO.

310
  Functions or subprocesses that return values doit ętre used as part of expressions. Only subprocesses that do not return any value may be invoked directly.

311
  La chaine passee a ConvertirANumero ne contient pas un nombre valide.
  * Verifiez que la valeur indiquee contient uniquement un nombre, avec eventuellement un signe et un point decimal.
312
  Les fonctions ASEN et ACOS ne peuvent etre appelees qu'avec une valeur comprise entre -1 et +1.
  * Verifiez la valeur de la variable ou de l'expression utilisee comme argument.
313
  La valeur entree pour cette variable n'est pas correcte.
  * Si c'est une erreur de saisie, corrigez la valeur entree dans le terminal.
  * La valeur attendue ici doit etre numerique et entiere.
  * Sinon, verifiez les definitions et expressions liees a cette variable.
320
  One of the expressions sur cette ligne that uses the negation opérateur (NO/~) has an operand on its left. But the negation opérateur is unary and its only operand doit ętre on the right.
  For example, in "No 5==x", the result "5==x" will be its operand; but in an expression like "a no b" tici is an error, since either the "a" should not be tici ("no b" is correct), or an operand is missing ("a y no b" is also correct).
  * Check whether tici is an operand before the negation in the expression.
  * Remove the operand or ajoutez le missing opérateur.
  It may also happen that the problem is due to a misunderstanding of opérateur precedence.
  * If the expression is complex, add parentheses to the subexpressions to alter/make explicit the desired precedence.

321
  The expression "De Otro Modo" is used only within a multiple-selection structure (<A href="segun.html">Según</A>). You are using "De Otro Modo" inside another type of structure, or outside any structure.
  * Check the nesting of your data structures and the correct placement of their FinXXX terminators
  Remarque: This expression doit ętre placé after the different options for the control variable, and indicates the path to follow when its value does not match any of the options. 

322
  You are trying to modify, through a read or assignment, the value of a variable that you should not modify. This is usually the case for the counter of a Para loop. Since the structure handles the counter automatically, the programmer should not modify it.
  * Vérifiez que you are not trying to read into or write to a variable that functions as the counter of a Para.
  * If your intention really was to modify the counter in order to alter how the Para works, you should consider replacing it with a different structure: Mientras or Repetir.

